In the Trial Room with Manifest™ is now live!

Our first trial begins at the house of Tarun Tahiliani, the master of modern drapes, to experience the drape, the drama, and the detail—up close.

With our muse Sharnamli Mehra (@sharnamli), we stepped into the master couturier's universe to explore what elegance looks like today—through two distinct bridal looks, styled multiple ways, each made for a different kind of bride. 

From corset mastery to draped lehenga saris—and sharp inputs from the experts—this episode is about helping you understand what works for your body, your style, and your moment.

This trial is just a preview of what’s in store at the FDCI Manifest Wedding Weekend.

Join us to witness Tarun Tahiliani’s latest creations in person, alongside some of India’s finest designers, in a showcase curated for the modern bride and groom.

📍 Taj Palace, New Delhi
🗓 2nd–3rd August

By RSVP only.

@taruntahiliani @fdciofficial
